      "parameters": {
        "mode": "runOnceForEachItem",
        "jsCode": "const candidate = $('🔧 Extraer candidatos del response').all()[$itemIndex].json;\n\nconst descClean = (candidate.vacancy_description || '')\n  .replace(/<[^>]*>/g, ' ')\n  .replace(/&amp;/g, '&')\n  .replace(/\\s+/g, ' ')\n  .substring(800, 3500);\n\nconst prompt = `You are a talent recruiter. Score this LinkedIn candidate for the job vacancy.\n\nVACANCY:\nTitle: ${candidate.vacancy_title}\nRequired skills: ${descClean}\n\nCANDIDATE:\nName: ${candidate.full_name}\nCurrent title: ${candidate.current_title}\nCurrent company: ${candidate.current_company || ''}\nJob title: ${candidate.job_title || ''}\nPrevious job: ${candidate.job_title2 || ''}\nLocation: ${candidate.city}\nAbout: ${candidate.additional_info || 'No info'}\n\nSCORING RULES:\n- Score 0-100\n- 80+ = strong match (right technologies, enough experience)\n- 50-79 = partial match (some skills but missing key ones)\n- 0-49 = poor match (student, bootcamp-only, no real experience)\n- Penalize: students, bootcamp-only, no real work experience\n- Reward: 5+ years, specific technologies matching vacancy, senior titles\n\nReturn ONLY raw JSON no markdown:\n{\"score\": 0, \"matched_keywords\": [\"kw1\"], \"reasoning\": \"brief\", \"urgency\": \"low|medium|high\", \"recommended_action\": \"contact|save|discard\", \"adtech_relevance\": \"low|medium|high\"}`;\n\nreturn {\n  json: {\n    ...candidate,\n    scoring_body: {\n      model: \"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\n      max_tokens: 300,\n      messages: [{ role: \"user\", content: prompt }]\n    }\n  }\n};"
      },
